**SPECIALIST RECOMMENDATIONS (pending human decision):**
- Prioritize north stairwell evacuations at Riverside Tower immediately.
- Extend North Warehouse exclusion radius to 400–600m once chemical identity 
confirmed.
- Route Riverside Tower evacuees **south and west** away from NE plume drift.
- Cease interior fire suppression at North Warehouse until chemical inventory 
